Package com.g1.mychess.player.dto

Class WhitelistDTO

java.lang.Object
com.g1.mychess.player.dto.WhitelistDTO
public class WhitelistDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) class for transferring information about a player's whitelist status. This class contains details such as player ID, username, email, and the reason for being whitelisted.
